<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>My First Web Page</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f7fb;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 14px;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1100px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      left: -999px;
      top: 10px;
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .skip-link:focus {
      left: 10px;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 80px 0 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    section {
      padding: 32px 0 60px;
    }

    .section-box {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-desc {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .grid-gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .flex-gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 18px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .flex-gallery img {
      width: 300px;
      flex: 1 1 250px;
    }

    .gallery img {
      height: 220px;
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .gallery img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px 0 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      nav ul {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 56px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">Skip to Main Content</a>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/100/100?random=1" alt="Website logo">
          <span>My Web Page</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#grid-section">Grid Gallery</a></li>
          <li><a href="#flex-section">Flex Gallery</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to My First Web Page</h1>
        <p>
          This website is a simple HTML and CSS practice project. It introduces basic layout techniques using sections, CSS Grid, and Flexbox in a clean and modern style.
        </p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn">Explore More</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-box">
          <h2 class="section-title">About This Page</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            Today I learn about HTML and CSS in Coursera by FPTU. This page is redesigned to look more modern, clear, and responsive on different screen sizes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="grid-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-box">
          <h2 class="section-title">Grid Gallery</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            This section uses CSS Grid to organize images in a balanced layout.
          </p>
          <div class="grid-gallery gallery">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=2" alt="Landscape image one">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=3" alt="Landscape image two">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=4" alt="Landscape image three">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?random=5" alt="Landscape image four">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="flex-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-box">
          <h2 class="section-title">Flex Gallery</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            This section uses Flexbox to arrange images in a flexible and responsive row.
          </p>
          <div class="flex-gallery gallery">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/150?random=6" alt="Flex gallery image one">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/150?random=7" alt="Flex gallery image two">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/150?random=8" alt="Flex gallery image three">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 My First Web Page. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
